00:00:29.480 --> 00:00:31.490 align:middle line:90%
It's available to everyone.

00:00:31.490 --> 00:00:35.900 align:middle line:84%
>> What we essentially are
is already fully awake,

00:00:35.900 --> 00:00:37.190 align:middle line:90%
fully aware.

00:00:37.190 --> 00:00:39.650 align:middle line:90%
>> And it's totally unlimited.

00:00:39.650 --> 00:00:45.620 align:middle line:84%
>> Your true nature is closer
than the you that you think you

00:00:45.620 --> 00:00:47.210 align:middle line:90%
are.

00:00:47.210 --> 00:00:50.840 align:middle line:84%
>> Complete, whole,
fulfilled, at peace.

