>> Consciousness is the ultimate
reality of the universe.

00:00:59.820 --> 00:01:01.370 align:middle line:90%
>> What is awakening anyway?

00:01:01.370 --> 00:01:03.584 align:middle line:90%
Somebody explain that to me.

00:01:03.584 --> 00:01:06.350 align:middle line:90%
[THEME MUSIC]

00:01:06.350 --> 00:01:29.610 align:middle line:90%


00:01:29.610 --> 00:01:33.370 align:middle line:90%
>> What is awakening?

00:01:33.370 --> 00:01:37.540 align:middle line:84%
