self, the imminent self,

00:01:37.540 --> 00:01:43.600 align:middle line:84%
or no self, or Buddha nature,
Dao or Christ consciousness,

00:01:43.600 --> 00:01:46.390 align:middle line:90%
it really doesn't matter.

00:01:46.390 --> 00:01:52.180 align:middle line:84%
In this film, we're going
to refer to it as awareness.

00:01:52.180 --> 00:01:55.990 align:middle line:84%
Awareness is not the
property of any religion.

00:01:55.990 --> 00:01:59.680 align:middle line:84%
Awakening or
realizing awareness is

00:01:59.680 --> 00:02:04.690 align:middle line:84%
like waking from a dream,
the dream of your character

00:02:04.690 --> 00:02:07.640 align:middle line:90%
in the play of life.

00:02:07.640 --> 00:02:10.550 align:middle line:84%
Through our characters,
we experience

00:02:10.550 --> 00:02:16.250 align:middle line:84%
the world in all of its
beauty and its ugliness.

00:02:16.250 --> 00:02:21.230 align:middle line:84%
We can call this experience
of life and death duality.

00:02:21.230 --> 00:02:26.570 align:middle line:84%
Around and around we go fixated
on the character's thoughts

00:02:26.570 --> 00:02:32.420 align:middle line:84%
and sensations, good and
bad, war and peace, light

00:02:32.420 --> 00:02:38.820 align:middle line:84%
and darkness, birth and death
until we wake up and find out

00:02:38.820 --> 00:02:40.530 align:middle line:90%
we are not the character.

00:02:40.530 --> 00:02:43.974 align:middle line:90%
[DRAMATIC MUSIC]

00:02:43.974 --> 00:03:09.120 align:middle line:90%


00:03:09.120 --> 00:03:12.930 align:middle line:10%
In this film, we are extending
an invitation for you

00:03:12.930 --> 00:03:16.620 align:middle line:10%
to directly experience
your true nature,

00:03:16.620 --> 00:03:24.210 align:middle line:10%
to find out directly not
intellectually who are you?

00:03:24.210 --> 00:03:29.280 align:middle line:84%
We will repeat this
invitation in different ways.

00:03:29.280 --> 00:03:33.690 align:middle line:84%
When inquiring into who
you are, let everything

00:03:33.690 --> 00:03:37.070 align:middle line:90%
be exactly as it is.

00:03:37.070 --> 00:03:41.090 align:middle line:84%
Don't move the mind to
make something happen

00:03:41.090 --> 00:03:44.810 align:middle line:84%
or to find some answer
on the level of mind

00:03:44.810 --> 00:03:48.530 align:middle line:84%
and yet don't try to
push away the mind.

00:03:48.530 --> 00:03:53.570 align:middle line:84%
Simply intend to directly
experience who you are,

00:03:53.570 --> 00:03:56.930 align:middle line:84%
letting the mind be
a don't-know mind.

00:03:56.930 --> 00:04:00.367 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:04:00.367 --> 00:04:08.230 align:middle line:90%


00:04:08.230 --> 00:04:12.820 align:middle line:10%
