delusion is that I

00:04:25.930 --> 00:04:28.720 align:middle line:10%
am this limited character.

00:04:28.720 --> 00:04:31.900 align:middle line:10%
>> When we're living from
a small separate self,

00:04:31.900 --> 00:04:36.470 align:middle line:10%
there's always some kind of
perpetual dissatisfaction.

00:04:36.470 --> 00:04:40.930 align:middle line:84%
