background feeling.

00:04:44.320 --> 00:04:45.980 align:middle line:90%
Something's not right.

00:04:45.980 --> 00:04:47.080 align:middle line:90%
Something's wrong.

00:04:47.080 --> 00:04:49.000 align:middle line:90%
I'm missing something.

