00:07:04.190 --> 00:07:06.630 align:middle line:84%
then I realized that
none of it mattered.

00:07:06.630 --> 00:07:08.960 align:middle line:84%
I woke up somewhere
around the age of 53

00:07:08.960 --> 00:07:12.900 align:middle line:90%
realizing none of this matters.

00:07:12.900 --> 00:07:14.330 align:middle line:90%
None of this means anything.

00:07:14.330 --> 00:07:19.190 align:middle line:84%
I was shocked to find how
little it really meant,

00:07:19.190 --> 00:07:20.960 align:middle line:90%
how pointless it all was.

00:07:20.960 --> 00:07:24.418 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

