00:11:20.560 --> 00:11:22.690 align:middle line:90%
but just a physical entity.

00:11:22.690 --> 00:11:25.810 align:middle line:84%
I'm born, I live, I die,
that's the beginning

00:11:25.810 --> 00:11:27.760 align:middle line:90%
and the end of it.

00:11:27.760 --> 00:11:34.370 align:middle line:84%
