00:11:34.370 --> 00:11:38.380 align:middle line:84%
Is it possible that I'm a
spiritual entity simply having

00:11:38.380 --> 00:11:39.940 align:middle line:90%
a physical experience?

00:11:39.940 --> 00:11:45.150 align:middle line:90%


00:11:45.150 --> 00:11:49.830 align:middle line:84%
>> Every experience in your
life has brought you to this one

00:11:49.830 --> 00:11:52.290 align:middle line:90%
universal question--

00:11:52.290 --> 00:11:53.520 align:middle line:90%
who are you?

00:11:53.520 --> 00:11:57.240 align:middle line:90%


00:11:57.240 --> 00:11:59.730 align:middle line:84%
