00:11:59.730 --> 00:12:03.110 align:middle line:90%


00:12:03.110 --> 00:12:06.755 align:middle line:84%
Let everything be
exactly as it is.

00:12:06.755 --> 00:12:11.060 align:middle line:90%


00:12:11.060 --> 00:12:12.905 align:middle line:90%
Who is aware of the mind?

00:12:12.905 --> 00:12:17.480 align:middle line:90%


00:12:17.480 --> 00:12:19.430 align:middle line:90%
