00:14:07.300 --> 00:14:08.860 align:middle line:84%
And the best way I
thought to do that

00:14:08.860 --> 00:14:10.810 align:middle line:84%
would be to study
artificial intelligence.

00:14:10.810 --> 00:14:15.910 align:middle line:84%
And so I went to MIT and was
in the artificial intelligence

00:14:15.910 --> 00:14:18.340 align:middle line:84%
