00:14:23.740 --> 00:14:25.780 align:middle line:84%
I wanted to see
what can machines do

00:14:25.780 --> 00:14:28.390 align:middle line:84%
and what's special if
anything about humans

00:14:28.390 --> 00:14:33.362 align:middle line:84%
and human neuroscience to
answer the very question,

00:14:33.362 --> 00:14:34.820 align:middle line:84%
are the spiritual
traditions right?

00:14:34.820 --> 00:14:36.820 align:middle line:90%
Are we more than just machines?

00:14:36.820 --> 00:14:39.670 align:middle line:84%
Or is the physicalist
scientific point

00:14:39.670 --> 00:14:41.710 align:middle line:84%
