that space and time is not

00:28:13.080 --> 00:28:14.160 align:middle line:90%
fundamental.

00:28:14.160 --> 00:28:17.070 align:middle line:84%
So the physicalist
interpretation of evolution

00:28:17.070 --> 00:28:18.090 align:middle line:90%
is wrong.

00:28:18.090 --> 00:28:22.230 align:middle line:84%
The idea that space and
time and particles somehow

00:28:22.230 --> 00:28:29.050 align:middle line:84%
