spacetime that's much richer,

00:28:34.360 --> 00:28:36.340 align:middle line:90%
the dynamics of consciousness.

00:28:36.340 --> 00:28:38.880 align:middle line:84%
What we do not do is throw
away our old theories.

00:28:38.880 --> 00:28:40.890 align:middle line:84%
