us back spacetime,

00:29:15.550 --> 00:29:17.380 align:middle line:84%
and gives us back
quantum theory,

00:29:17.380 --> 00:29:19.720 align:middle line:84%
and gives us back special
and general relativity,

00:29:19.720 --> 00:29:22.420 align:middle line:84%
