that when you finally awaken,

00:41:26.740 --> 00:41:29.710 align:middle line:84%
you realize that
all of the practices

00:41:29.710 --> 00:41:34.540 align:middle line:84%
were being done by the false
self, the character in the VR

00:41:34.540 --> 00:41:41.500 align:middle line:84%
game, and that you, the
true self, was never bound.

00:41:41.500 --> 00:41:45.970 align:middle line:84%
All you have to do is give up
the preferences of the ego,

00:41:45.970 --> 00:41:50.300 align:middle line:84%
to give up the
fixation on things.

00:41:50.300 --> 00:41:53.720 align:middle line:84%
Anything within the field
of changing phenomena

00:41:53.720 --> 00:41:56.046 align:middle line:90%
is not the true self.

00:41:56.046 --> 00:42:00.140 align:middle line:84%
The you that you think you
are, the you that you've always

00:42:00.140 --> 00:42:03.230 align:middle line:84%
been identified with
will never awaken.

00:42:03.230 --> 00:42:06.260 align:middle line:90%
You awaken from that character.

00:42:06.260 --> 00:42:09.230 align:middle line:84%
You awaken from the
delusion that you

00:42:09.230 --> 00:42:10.950 align:middle line:90%
are this conditioned character.

00:42:10.950 --> 00:42:15.290 align:middle line:84%
So when people come to these
retreats, they think this I,

00:42:15.290 --> 00:42:17.270 align:middle line:84%
this little me is
going to awaken,

00:42:17.270 --> 00:42:19.080 align:middle line:84%
some great thing
is going to happen.

00:42:19.080 --> 00:42:22.310 align:middle line:84%
But at a certain point, that
little me will never do it.

00:42:22.310 --> 00:42:23.330 align:middle line:90%
It has to give up.

00:42:23.330 --> 00:42:24.530 align:middle line:90%
It has to fail.

00:42:24.530 --> 00:42:29.000 align:middle line:84%
And it's only in that failure
we realize who we are,

00:42:29.000 --> 00:42:33.300 align:middle line:84%
that we've always been aware,
we've always been present.

00:42:33.300 --> 00:42:36.050 align:middle line:84%
We just got hooked
into this character

00:42:36.050 --> 00:42:39.044 align:middle line:90%
and we believed we were that.

00:42:39.044 --> 00:42:42.488 align:middle line:90%
[DRAMATIC MUSIC]

00:42:42.488 --> 00:42:49.380 align:middle line:90%


00:42:49.380 --> 00:42:54.750 align:middle line:84%
>> I started my spiritual
search in the classical Advaita

00:42:54.750 --> 00:43:00.930 align:middle line:84%
Vedanta tradition, which was a
devotional path that involved

00:43:00.930 --> 00:43:05.460 align:middle line:84%
mantra meditation, which I
practiced very diligently

00:43:05.460 --> 00:43:06.990 align:middle line:90%
for 20 years.

00:43:06.990 --> 00:43:12.480 align:middle line:84%
And mantra meditation involves
focusing your attention

00:43:12.480 --> 00:43:17.680 align:middle line:84%
on a sound and then
gradually the sound fades.

00:43:17.680 --> 00:43:21.190 align:middle line:84%
However, it was
really when I came

00:43:21.190 --> 00:43:29.560 align:middle line:84%
in touch with the direct path
that my spiritual search really

00:43:29.560 --> 00:43:31.660 align:middle line:90%
reached its culmination.

00:43:31.660 --> 00:43:35.710 align:middle line:84%
Because in this
direct approach, we

00:43:35.710 --> 00:43:40.270 align:middle line:84%
don't give our attention to
any object however subtle,

00:43:40.270 --> 00:43:44.110 align:middle line:84%
for instance, a mantra,
a sound, the breath.

00:43:44.110 --> 00:43:48.820 align:middle line:84%
We allow our attention to
sink inwards or backwards

00:43:48.820 --> 00:43:51.670 align:middle line:90%
into its source.

00:43:51.670 --> 00:43:54.920 align:middle line:90%
>> Let's use an analogy.

00:43:54.920 --> 00:43:57.650 align:middle line:84%
Imagine that you were watching
your life on a television

00:43:57.650 --> 00:43:58.450 align:middle line:90%
screen.

00:43:58.450 --> 00:44:02.650 align:middle line:84%
You are identified with the
character on the screen.

00:44:02.650 --> 00:44:05.740 align:middle line:84%
Day after day, year
after year, you

00:44:05.740 --> 00:44:08.620 align:middle line:84%
are involved with the
story of the character

00:44:08.620 --> 00:44:12.250 align:middle line:84%
when suddenly you wake
up out of the story

00:44:12.250 --> 00:44:16.040 align:middle line:84%
to notice the screen on
which the character appears

00:44:16.040 --> 00:44:19.130 align:middle line:84%
and you realize you are
not the character you

00:44:19.130 --> 00:44:20.810 align:middle line:90%
have been watching.

00:44:20.810 --> 00:44:25.940 align:middle line:84%
Objects can come and go on the
screen, characters come and go,

00:44:25.940 --> 00:44:29.270 align:middle line:84%
but the screen
remains unchanged.

00:44:29.270 --> 00:44:34.190 align:middle line:84%
The character can get wet,
the screen does not get wet.

00:44:34.190 --> 00:44:37.490 align:middle line:84%
The character can be
disturbed, but the screen

00:44:37.490 --> 00:44:39.510 align:middle line:90%
is not disturbed.

00:44:39.510 --> 00:44:41.910 align:middle line:84%
Without the screen,
the characters

00:44:41.910 --> 00:44:46.020 align:middle line:84%
would not exist yet the
screen goes unnoticed.

00:44:46.020 --> 00:44:50.670 align:middle line:10%
The characters go about
their scripted lives.

00:44:50.670 --> 00:44:53.400 align:middle line:90%
Awareness is like the screen.

00:44:53.400 --> 00:44:57.540 align:middle line:84%
It is like the space in
which all thoughts, motions,

00:44:57.540 --> 00:45:01.350 align:middle line:84%
all states of
consciousness come and go.

00:45:01.350 --> 00:45:05.700 align:middle line:10%
Thoughts, sensations, and
the entire outside world

00:45:05.700 --> 00:45:09.160 align:middle line:10%
appear on the screen
constantly changing,

00:45:09.160 --> 00:45:10.905 align:middle line:10%
but the screen does not change.

00:45:10.905 --> 00:45:13.900 align:middle line:90%


00:45:13.900 --> 00:45:17.710 align:middle line:84%
It's the mind that
changes states

00:45:17.710 --> 00:45:19.750 align:middle line:90%
through the human experience.

00:45:19.750 --> 00:45:24.730 align:middle line:84%
But there's something that
which you are that remains,

00:45:24.730 --> 00:45:30.040 align:middle line:84%
something that is ever present
that is aware of those changing

00:45:30.040 --> 00:45:35.365 align:middle line:84%
states and that is consciousness
or our true nature.

00:45:35.365 --> 00:45:38.800 align:middle line:84%
As long as there is attachment
to a character on the screen,

00:45:38.800 --> 00:45:41.890 align:middle line:84%
a sense that I am
that character, then

00:45:41.890 --> 00:45:47.500 align:middle line:84%
there will be suffering, Maya,
the illusion of the self.

00:45:47.500 --> 00:45:50.620 align:middle line:84%
Nothing you can do as
the dream character

00:45:50.620 --> 00:45:53.800 align:middle line:84%
will help to free you
whether you follow

00:45:53.800 --> 00:45:57.220 align:middle line:84%
the script in the drama
of your life or rebel

00:45:57.220 --> 00:45:58.330 align:middle line:90%
against the script.

00:45:58.330 --> 00:46:01.360 align:middle line:84%
If you act from the point
of view of the character,

00:46:01.360 --> 00:46:04.630 align:middle line:84%
then you're caught
in the illusion.

00:46:04.630 --> 00:46:11.790 align:middle line:84%
To awaken, stop identifying
with what appears on the screen.

00:46:11.790 --> 00:46:14.850 align:middle line:84%
Recognize that it
is all impermanent.

00:46:14.850 --> 00:46:20.040 align:middle line:84%
Stop reacting to thoughts and
treating the program as real.

00:46:20.040 --> 00:46:23.700 align:middle line:84%
If I withdraw attention
from the screen turning

00:46:23.700 --> 00:46:28.650 align:middle line:84%
awareness towards itself, an
unfathomable thing happens.

00:46:28.650 --> 00:46:30.825 align:middle line:90%
Awareness itself wakes up.

00:46:30.825 --> 00:46:34.310 align:middle line:90%


00:46:34.310 --> 00:46:36.490 align:middle line:90%
This is not a happening.

00:46:36.490 --> 00:46:40.270 align:middle line:84%
Happening is what
happens on the screen.

00:46:40.270 --> 00:46:43.540 align:middle line:84%
Awakening is just
recognizing the screen

00:46:43.540 --> 00:46:47.270 align:middle line:90%
that was always already there.

00:46:47.270 --> 00:46:50.540 align:middle line:84%
Do not believe
your next thought.

00:46:50.540 --> 00:46:55.310 align:middle line:84%
Instead, turn awareness
towards awareness itself.

